{
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6901_1001_0100_10": "[Name:PlayerNickname ]。\n您辛苦了！",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6901_1001_0200_10": "其實是有一個地方，\n我想讓您和鳴依一起看看……",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0100_10": "哇！好棒的地方呀！\n這裡是……？",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0200_10": "是的，這裡叫做\n訓練家沙龍！",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0300_10": "是專門開放給訓練家們\n自由交流同樂的地方。",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0400_10": "為什麼會有這樣的地方……？",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0500_10": "因為帕希歐有來自\n四面八方的訓練家們……",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0600_10": "所以我們想讓隊伍成員\n或互相還不熟悉的訓練家們，\n在這裡進一步加深彼此的感情。",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6902_1001_0700_10": "就是這樣。[Name:PlayerNickname ]您\n也請盡情在這裡和\n各位訓練家增進感情吧！",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6903_1001_0100_10": "原來如此。\n增進感情呀……",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6903_1001_0200_10": "這樣的話，\n[Name:PlayerNickname ]！",
    "intro_only_event_pasiosalon_tutorial/6903_1001_0300_10": "我們就趕快來試著\n增進感情吧！"
}
